<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/web3/1.5.2/web3.min.js"></script>
    <title>Dashboard</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-image: url('https://wallpapercave.com/wp/wp2337027.jpg'); /* Background image URL */
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            color: #333; /* Dark text color */
        }

        .welcome {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 50px;
            font-size: 32px; /* Increased font size */
            color: #fff; /* White text color */
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5); /* Text shadow */
        }

        .container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            align-items: flex-start;
            margin-top: 50px;
        }

        .content-section {
            flex: 1;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.167); /* Semi-transparent white background */
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3); /* Box shadow */
        }

        .image-section {
            flex: 1;
            padding: 20px;
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .image-section img {
            max-width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            margin: 10px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5); /* Box shadow */
        }

        .advantages {
            margin-top: 50px;
            color: #fff; /* White text color */
        }

        .advantages h2 {
            color: #1E90FF; /* Blue heading color */
        }

        .advantages ul {
            list-style-type: none;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .advantages li {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .advantages li:before {
            content: "âœ“ ";
            color: #1E90FF; /* Blue checkmark color */
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-right: 5px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1 class="welcome">Welcome to  Future of Privacy </h1>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="content-section">
            <!-- Place your content here -->
            <div class="advantages">
                
                <ul>
                    <li>Decentralization: No central authority controls the network.</li>
                    <li>Security: Data is encrypted and stored across multiple nodes, making it highly secure.</li>
                    <li>Transparency: All transactions are recorded on a public ledger, ensuring transparency.</li>
                    <li>Trustless Transactions: Transactions can be made without the need for intermediaries.</li>
                    <li>Immutable Records: Once recorded, data cannot be altered or tampered with.</li>
                    <li>Smart Contracts: Self-executing contracts with predefined conditions.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="image-section">
            <img src="https://technicalistechnical.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/aa-768x543.jpg" alt="Blockchain Image">
            <!-- Add more images as needed -->
        </div>
    </div>
    <script>
        setTimeout(() => {
            window.location.href = '/loc12.html'; // Redirect to loc1.html after 20 seconds
        }, 5000); // 20000 milliseconds = 20 seconds
    </script>
</body>
</html>
